subtitleNullable: Floating Car Data points collected in four Italian cities
descriptionNullable:
### Context

This dataset contains FCD points collected from four Italian cities: Milan, Naples, Rome, and Turin. This data can be used for time series analysis and geospatial analysis.

### Content

The data presented here has already been processed for time series analysis. Each row contains a single trajectory of 20 points separated by a fixed time-step of 60 seconds. Points are expressed as (x, y) coordinates.

### Acknowledgements

This data has been acquired and pre-processed by VEM Solutions Spa (www.vemsolutions.it).
